name: Diff
comment:
Functions to compare strings to produce a list of changes.  This is an
implementation of the [Hunt-McIlroy](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hunt%E2%80%93McIlroy_algorithm)
diff algorithm.

# Types and Constructors
@docs Change

# Diffing text
@docs diffChars, diffLines

values.name: diffChars
values.comment: Diffs two strings, comparing character by character.

values.name: diffLines
values.comment: Diffs two strings, comparing line by line.
